@baseUrl = http://localhost:8001

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Create Submission - Anonymous
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/submissions/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "company": "WSO2",
  "role": "Software Engineer",
  "level": "Mid",
  "country": "Sri Lanka",
  "city": "Colombo",
  "salary_amount": 750000,
  "currency": "LKR",
  "experience_years": 3,
  "anonymize": false
}

