### Get All Submissions
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/submissions/

### Get All Submissions - With Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/submissions/?skip=0&limit=10

### Get Submission By ID (replace with actual UUID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/submissions/REPLACE_WITH_UUID

### Get Non-Existent Submission (should return 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/submissions/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000